276
00:15:28,949 --> 00:15:30,447
It's nothing.

277
00:15:30,619 --> 00:15:32,188
She's clean.

278
00:15:33,374 --> 00:15:37,471
It's good news.
You don't show any signs
of coronary artery disease.

279
00:15:37,690 --> 00:15:38,795
