I think I got a couple of blueberries.

334
00:19:07,737 --> 00:19:10,564
Nope. Sorry. Just one.

335
00:19:12,728 --> 00:19:14,697
Oh, don't look all weepy.

336
00:19:15,154 --> 00:19:17,358
You got a problem with me,
deal with it.

337
00:19:17,442 --> 00:19:19,233
Short my sheets or something.

338
00:19:19,658 --> 00:19:21,214
[Sighs]

339
