466
00:26:30,030 --> 00:26:31,868
This isn't a college dorm.

467
00:26:31,978 --> 00:26:33,184
It could be.

468
00:26:33,368 --> 00:26:35,079
We're not 18!

469
00:26:35,178 --> 00:26:36,295
So what?

470
00:26:36,379 --> 00:26:37,444
What did I do to you?

471
00:26:37,528 --> 00:26:40,879
