474
00:26:45,113 --> 00:26:47,041
Oh, so this is therapy?

475
00:26:47,125 --> 00:26:51,289
No. It's just...
makes me smile.

476
00:26:51,828 --> 00:26:53,842
All right, I'm finding
a new place tomorrow.

477
00:26:53,926 --> 00:26:56,327
Right, but not tonight.
[Pops cork]

478
00:26:56,389 --> 00:26:59,335
Well, I figure you wanna shave
my eyebrows while I'm asleep.

479
00:26:59,424 --> 00:27:01,570
I wouldn't wanna
deprive you of that last smile.

480
00:27:01,675 --> 00:27:03,160
You're not going anywhere.

481
00:27:03,244 --> 00:27:04,816
You're gonna sit on my couch,

482
00:27:04,928 --> 00:27:08,430
